observations.recommendation:
We recommended the Municipal Mayor to:

direct the Municipal Engineering Office to submit disbursement vouchers together with copies of Certificate of Completion/Statement of Work Accomplished (SWA) on completed projects to the Municipal Accountant for processing and proper recording in the books of accounts;

advise the Municipal Accountant to reclassify completed projects into the appropriate asset account based on the submitted documents by the Municipal Engineering Office to its related PPE, and;

Recognize the related depreciation expense and accumulated depreciation for the said projects from the time they were available for use.

